29
00:02:45,875 --> 00:02:47,535
Just wait and see.

30
00:02:47,535 --> 00:02:48,880
Sure.

31
00:02:49,545 --> 00:02:51,165
Go ahead and do that.

32
00:02:51,165 --> 00:02:53,915
Do it right now. I'm curious, too.

33
00:02:53,915 --> 00:02:56,925
Hold on, hold on, hold on.

34
00:02:56,925 --> 00:03:01,405
What's this? You really didn't give her that money?

35
00:03:02,015 --> 00:03:06,345
Where did she get so much money if it wasn't you?

36
00:03:06,345 --> 00:03:08,990
So, Ms. Kim has been...

37
00:03:09,615 --> 00:03:13,265
seeing you because of money all this time,

38
00:03:13,265 --> 00:03:17,785
but she wanted to end things by giving you this money.

39
00:03:17,785 --> 00:03:19,845
That's what you're saying, right?

40
00:03:22,305 --> 00:03:26,085
Do you two think I'm an idiot or something?

41
00:03:26,085 --> 00:03:31,545
Hey, you think you could fool me like this?

42
00:03:31,545 --> 00:03:34,385
I'll get to the bottom of this.

43
00:03:34,385 --> 00:03:38,515
And I'm warning you right now.

44
00:03:38,515 --> 00:03:41,685
Don't try to come between Kim Ji Yeong and me.

45
00:03:41,685 --> 00:03:43,495
You got that?

46
