You said you had something to tell me.

50
00:04:07,155 --> 00:04:08,825
What is it?

51
00:04:09,905 --> 00:04:12,195
Grandma,

52
00:04:12,195 --> 00:04:16,485
I took out 300 million from your account and used it.

53
00:04:17,105 --> 00:04:21,675
