54
00:04:21,675 --> 00:04:23,740
So I'm reporting to you.

55
00:04:24,245 --> 00:04:27,025
I'm sorry I couldn't tell you first.

56
00:04:27,025 --> 00:04:31,585
Ji Yeong, why would you be sorry?

57
00:04:31,585 --> 00:04:34,595
I said it's all yours.

58
00:04:34,595 --> 00:04:37,645
I'm sure you used it for a reason.

59
00:04:37,645 --> 00:04:40,915
