67
00:05:05,305 --> 00:05:07,965
I was just guessing you were.

68
00:05:07,965 --> 00:05:11,455
But it was true.

69
00:05:11,455 --> 00:05:13,955
Yes, Grandma.

70
00:05:13,955 --> 00:05:18,395
I dated him because he paid off Ahjumma's private loan.

71
00:05:18,395 --> 00:05:22,485
But it just didn't feel right, so I paid him back.

72
00:05:22,485 --> 00:05:26,745
Yes, well done. Well done.

73
00:05:26,745 --> 00:05:29,935
You need to pay off money like that quickly.

74
00:05:29,935 --> 00:05:36,405
Otherwise, you get taken advantage of for the rest of your life.

75
00:05:36,405 --> 00:05:40,465
You can't live a low life like that.

76
00:05:40,465 --> 00:05:42,535
Well done. Well done.

77
00:05:44,305 --> 00:05:49,905
I'm so relieved to hear you say that, Grandma.

78
00:05:49,905 --> 00:05:51,525
Goodness...

79
00:05:52,445 --> 00:05:54,245
Grandma,

80
00:05:55,375 --> 00:06:00,205
I'll work hard and pay you back everything.

81
00:06:00,205 --> 00:06:06,235
Gosh, I told you not to worry about that.

82
00:06:09,135 --> 00:06:13,895
But you still need to make a lot of money.

83
00:06:14,565 --> 00:06:16,535
Okay, Grandma.

84
00:06:16,535 --> 00:06:20,695
I'll make a lot of money and give you everything. Everything.

85
00:06:20,695 --> 00:06:23,745
Gosh, yes. Yes, yes, yes.

86
00:06:23,745 --> 00:06:27,475
Aigoo, sweetheart. My sweetheart.

87
00:06:27,475 --> 00:06:29,165
Don't be sick, Grandma.

88
00:06:29,165 --> 00:06:33,035
Okay. Let's be healthy.

89
00:06:34,725 --> 00:06:37,725
Aigoo, my sweetheart.

90
