102
00:07:28,735 --> 00:07:32,435
It breaks my heart whenever I think about that.

103
00:07:34,725 --> 00:07:39,895
Director, Ji Yeong has no feelings for him.

104
00:07:39,895 --> 00:07:45,155
I've never seen Ji Yeong smile even once while seeing him.

105
00:07:46,445 --> 00:07:52,100
Director, you know why I'm telling you this,

106
00:07:52,100 --> 00:07:53,920
right?

107
00:07:53,925 --> 00:07:55,375
Pardon?

108
00:07:56,385 --> 00:07:58,065
Well, yes.

109
00:07:58,755 --> 00:08:02,735
Thank you so much for telling me, ma'am.

110
00:08:04,195 --> 00:08:08,915
She must've suffered a lot. This is a relief.

111
00:08:10,695 --> 00:08:18,120
By the way, you don't seem that happy about it for some reason.

112
00:08:18,775 --> 00:08:23,485
No, I'm happy. Of course I am.

113
00:08:31,245 --> 00:08:34,735
Grandma, should we make bibimguksu?

114
00:08:34,735 --> 00:08:37,375
With radish kimchi?

115
