Where did she go?

118
00:08:59,515 --> 00:09:01,185
Grandma!

119
00:09:01,765 --> 00:09:03,395
Grandma!

120
00:09:04,195 --> 00:09:05,935
What happened?

121
00:09:05,935 --> 00:09:08,575
She was definitely sleeping earlier.

122
00:09:16,645 --> 00:09:20,425
Grandma, where are you right now?

123
00:09:22,595 --> 00:09:26,225
What did you say? In front of the house?

124
00:09:26,225 --> 00:09:30,565
She's about to run outside because she's surprised.

125
00:09:30,565 --> 00:09:32,465
My gosh.

126
00:09:33,795 --> 00:09:38,505
Wait, what are you doing here, Director?

127
00:09:40,315 --> 00:09:43,485
Grandma, what happened?

128
00:09:43,485 --> 00:09:46,685
I thought you were sleeping in the room.

129
00:09:46,685 --> 00:09:52,255
I suggested to him that we get Americano together.

130
00:09:52,255 --> 00:09:55,295
You should've told me you were doing that, then.

131
00:09:55,295 --> 00:09:59,195
I almost had a heart attack thinking you were missing.

132
00:09:59,195 --> 00:10:01,775
That's what the phone is for.

133
00:10:01,775 --> 00:10:06,135
You put a chain on me like this. Why do you worry?

134
00:10:06,135 --> 00:10:10,015
Ji Yeong, here are housewarming gifts.

135
00:10:12,105 --> 00:10:14,785
I hope everything goes well living here.

136
00:10:14,785 --> 00:10:17,995
Thank you.

137
00:10:17,995 --> 00:10:23,415
Ji Yeong, will you just stand out here like this?

138
00:10:24,315 --> 00:10:30,765
Director, why don't you eat kongguksu* with us inside? 
  (Soybean noodles) 

139
00:10:30,765 --> 00:10:34,870
You bought me an Americano today.

140
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:38,230
I should return the favor somehow.

141
00:10:41,205 --> 00:10:44,425
I'll take a rain check today, Grandma.

142
00:10:44,425 --> 00:10:47,180
I'll come back when I get a chance next time.

143
00:10:47,705 --> 00:10:50,195
That's too bad, then.

144
00:10:50,195 --> 00:10:52,535
Go inside, Grandma. I'll leave now.

145
00:10:52,535 --> 00:10:56,235
Okay, Director. Get home safely.

146
00:10:56,235 --> 00:10:58,555
Goodbye.

147
00:11:30,695 --> 00:11:34,585
Grandma, you told the Director all that?

148
00:11:34,585 --> 00:11:37,055
Why would you say something like that to him?

149
00:11:37,055 --> 00:11:39,365
What's the big deal, exactly?

150
00:11:39,365 --> 00:11:45,525
