00:20:13,725 --> 00:20:16,355
I've been so petty.

265
00:20:17,885 --> 00:20:22,475
When you two came to my office,

266
00:20:22,475 --> 00:20:25,935
I finally realized that...

267
00:20:26,675 --> 00:20:29,060
I did something seriously wrong.

268
00:20:29,595 --> 00:20:34,945
I sincerely apologize for what I did then.

269
00:20:36,535 --> 00:20:42,485
Don't mention it. You made Pil Sung the CEO of Go Go Entertainment.

270
00:20:42,485 --> 00:20:51,025
We're actually grateful that you approved his abilities.

271
00:20:51,725 --> 00:20:57,700
I'm so grateful that you acknowledged Ma Ri as Pil Sung's little sister.

272
00:20:57,700 --> 00:21:02,315
Really, thank you so much.

273
00:21:02,315 --> 00:21:05,315
No, not at all.

274
00:21:05,315 --> 00:21:10,215
Pil Sung deeply cares about Ma Ri.

275
00:21:10,215 --> 00:21:17,705
We're grateful to you for acknowledging Pil Sung as Ma Ri's brother.

276
00:21:19,295 --> 00:21:23,435
Ma Ri has a big brother now, and the two of them get along so well.

277
00:21:23,435 --> 00:21:26,595
It makes me so happy.

278
00:21:27,395 --> 00:21:36,055
I hope our families get along as one family from now on.

279
00:21:37,015 --> 00:21:40,045
We share a child together.

280
00:21:41,905 --> 00:21:43,625
Of course. Of course.

281
00:21:43,625 --> 00:21:47,035
We should treat each other as a family from now on.

282
00:21:47,035 --> 00:21:50,935
I decided to become friends with Ma Ri,

283
00:21:50,935 --> 00:21:56,275
but I really think of her as my granddaughter.

284
00:21:58,845 --> 00:22:01,105
Thank you so much.

285
00:22:27,152 --> 00:22:28,752
What's going on?

286
00:22:28,752 --> 00:22:34,667
The chairman of APP Group wants us to consider them family.

287
00:22:34,667 --> 00:22:36,832
He said we share a child together.

288
00:22:36,832 --> 00:22:39,932
And he thanked us for raising Pil Sung well.

289
00:22:39,932 --> 00:22:43,222
You can tell how generous he is.

290
00:22:43,222 --> 00:22:46,902
No wonder he's able to lead a big company like that.

291
00:22:46,902 --> 00:22:50,092
He's on another level than normal people like us.

292
00:22:50,092 --> 00:22:52,087
Mom, catch your breathe while talking.

293
00:22:52,087 --> 00:22:54,877
You'll suffocate.

294
00:22:54,882 --> 00:22:59,612
Isn't Chairman Gong a true gentleman?

295
00:22:59,612 --> 00:23:02,442
He forgave his wife without divorcing her.

296
00:23:02,442 --> 00:23:06,752
And he even acknowledged her son, Pil Sung, as Ma Ri's brother.

297
00:23:06,752 --> 00:23:08,572
I think differently of him now.

298
00:23:08,572 --> 00:23:11,862
He really is extraordinary.

299
00:23:11,862 --> 00:23:15,362
I know. He even visited us.

300
00:23:15,362 --> 00:23:18,102
I do feel grateful.

301
00:23:18,102 --> 00:23:19,847
Honey,

302
00:23:20,877 --> 00:23:27,617
I think he came because he wants you and Soo Yeon to get along again.

303
00:23:27,622 --> 00:23:29,677
Yes, Seon Yeong.

304
00:23:29,677 --> 00:23:33,237
You should make up with Seon Yeon, too.

305
00:23:33,242 --> 00:23:35,582
Although it'd be hard to go back to the way it was.

306
00:23:35,582 --> 00:23:39,382
And Chairman Gong likes your shikhye*.
  (Korean dessert drink) 

307
00:23:39,382 --> 00:23:42,952
Make yakbab*, too, and take them over. 
  (Sweet rice with nuts and jujubes) 

308
00:23:43,982 --> 00:23:46,862
Yes, I'll think about it.

309
00:23:52,262 --> 00:23:56,012
What important matter did you want to talk about? Even asking me to come here.

310
00:23:57,042 --> 00:23:59,182
Earlier today,

311
00:23:59,662 --> 00:24:02,182
I stopped by Seon Yeong's house.

312
00:24:03,512 --> 00:24:07,862
Y-You were at Seon Yeong's house?

313
00:24:07,862 --> 00:24:10,612
Why did you do that without telling me?

314
00:24:11,312 --> 00:24:16,442
I need to adopt Pil Sung as my son.

315
00:24:17,522 --> 00:24:19,452
Honey.

316
00:24:19,452 --> 00:24:23,322
Why are you so shocked? I told you.

317
00:24:23,322 --> 00:24:26,442
If he's your son, he's my son, too.

318
00:24:27,022 --> 00:24:30,392
Did you tell Seon Yeong's family that, by chance?

319
00:24:30,392 --> 00:24:33,432
I wouldn't be so careless.

320
00:24:34,012 --> 00:24:36,292
I just checked their reaction this time.

321
00:24:36,292 --> 00:24:40,202
I need to know what they think of us

322
00:24:40,202 --> 00:24:43,262
so I can bring up the adoption later.

323
00:24:43,262 --> 00:24:48,372
It looks like they're a lot less upset with you, too.

324
00:24:48,372 --> 00:24:53,572
I think they think of Pil Sung as Ma Ri's brother, too.

325
00:24:54,432 --> 00:24:58,682
Honey, but it still doesn't feel right.

326
00:24:59,542 --> 00:25:01,632
I've thought about this a lot, too.

327
00:25:01,632 --> 00:25:04,262
I'm not just saying this lightly.

328
00:25:04,862 --> 00:25:07,452
As you know,

329
00:25:07,452 --> 00:25:11,142
I've always liked Pil Sung.

330
00:25:11,712 --> 00:25:13,607
I found him to be...

331
00:25:14,222 --> 00:25:17,792
reliable since he was in high school.

332
00:25:18,512 --> 00:25:21,742
I liked him so much that...

333
00:25:21,742 --> 00:25:27,607
I wanted him to be with Ma Ri without knowing he was her brother.

334
00:25:28,642 --> 00:25:30,372
Honey,

335
00:25:31,492 --> 00:25:35,832
I want Pil Sung so badly.

336
00:25:36,632 --> 00:25:40,092
