337
00:25:40,092 --> 00:25:44,752
I don't want to hurt her even more.

338
00:25:44,752 --> 00:25:46,582
Honey,

339
00:25:47,112 --> 00:25:49,432
this isn't a bad thing.

340
00:25:49,432 --> 00:25:52,402
We aren't taking him from them.

341
00:25:52,402 --> 00:25:54,512
Our families will become one.

342
00:25:54,512 --> 00:25:58,212
It's a great thing for both families.

343
00:25:58,212 --> 00:25:59,892
Honey,

344
00:26:01,252 --> 00:26:03,872
I'll take care of everything.

345
00:26:03,872 --> 00:26:06,822
Just promise me that...

346
00:26:06,822 --> 00:26:10,282
you'll be on my side, no matter what.

347
00:26:10,282 --> 00:26:15,602
Pil Sung is the only one who would protect Ma Ri.

348
00:26:21,702 --> 00:26:23,412
All right.

349
00:26:23,412 --> 00:26:25,452
I'll do that.

350
00:26:39,512 --> 00:26:41,422
 The customer is not answering the phone. 

351
00:26:41,422 --> 00:26:45,582
 You'll be connected to the voicemail after the beep. 

352
00:26:46,502 --> 00:26:48,932
What's going on?

353
00:26:48,932 --> 00:26:53,492
She won't answer my calls, and she won't read my messages, either.

354
00:26:53,492 --> 00:26:58,242
By chance, did she block me?

355
00:26:59,082 --> 00:27:00,752
This woman...

356
00:27:00,752 --> 00:27:03,082
What's with her?

357
00:27:04,852 --> 00:27:08,642
Secretary Jo, find out Kim Ji Yeong's schedule.

358
00:27:08,642 --> 00:27:12,622
I'm so sorry for causing a commotion during our first shoot.

359
00:27:12,622 --> 00:27:15,562
I think it happened because I was so nervous.

360
00:27:15,562 --> 00:27:18,502
I'll make sure it doesn't happen again.

361
00:27:18,502 --> 00:27:23,192
I'll work harder and do my best from now on.

362
00:27:23,842 --> 00:27:25,422
I'm so sorry.

363
00:27:25,422 --> 00:27:28,902
 It's okay. It's okay. 

364
00:27:28,902 --> 00:27:30,472
 It's okay. 

365
00:27:30,472 --> 00:27:34,332
Let's think that the worst is over with.

366
00:27:34,332 --> 00:27:36,482
Let's keep moving forward.

367
00:27:36,482 --> 00:27:39,112
Let's create a masterpiece that will shock the world!

368
00:27:39,112 --> 00:27:40,572
"Seoul Lady," fighting!

369
00:27:40,572 --> 00:27:42,962
 Fighting! 

370
00:27:43,732 --> 00:27:46,462
- Fighting. 
 - Fighting.

371
00:27:48,012 --> 00:27:50,692
I'll go talk to the film crew.

372
00:27:50,692 --> 00:27:52,052
Have a seat here, Director.

373
00:27:52,052 --> 00:27:54,292
You seem like a totally different person today, Ji Yeong.

374
00:27:54,292 --> 00:27:57,252
Your style, facial expressions, and the way you talk, too.

375
00:27:57,252 --> 00:28:00,512
You're totally different from Kim Ji Yeong in "House of Roses."

376
00:28:00,512 --> 00:28:04,252
I agree. You've completely become Bun Hong.

377
00:28:04,252 --> 00:28:06,032
You're totally a Seoul Lady now.

378
00:28:06,032 --> 00:28:07,942
Thank you.

379
00:28:07,942 --> 00:28:12,512
Ji Yeong, you must've gone through a lot.

380
00:28:12,512 --> 00:28:15,712
 Eat as much as you'd like and order more. 

381
00:28:15,712 --> 00:28:18,902
- Eat this and cheer up. 
 - Thank you.

382
00:28:22,742 --> 00:28:26,542
- Isn't it tasty? 
 - Yes, it's so tasty.

383
00:28:26,542 --> 00:28:29,072
Eating this cheers me up.

384
00:28:31,512 --> 00:28:34,322
It must've been difficult because of the heat.

385
00:28:34,322 --> 00:28:36,452
Not at all.

386
00:28:36,452 --> 00:28:39,462
I really liked the camera angle last time.

387
00:28:47,082 --> 00:28:51,242
 Oppa came such a long way. 

388
00:28:51,242 --> 00:28:54,392
 He was a cute assistant director then. 

389
00:28:54,392 --> 00:28:57,932
 But now, he has become a really cool director. 

390
00:29:04,592 --> 00:29:09,202
