391
00:29:09,202 --> 00:29:12,682
- Please don't be mad if you don't see me later. 
 - Okay.

392
00:29:12,682 --> 00:29:15,952
I'll explain it to the Director.

393
00:29:22,202 --> 00:29:27,222
Ji Yeong, you won't answer my calls, and you ignore my messages.

394
00:29:27,222 --> 00:29:29,267
