396
00:29:33,872 --> 00:29:38,232
President Gong, I have nothing to say to you.

397
00:29:40,552 --> 00:29:42,922
Do you think I'm a toy?

398
00:29:43,622 --> 00:29:46,992
You leeched off me when you needed money.

399
00:29:46,992 --> 00:29:49,892
