402
00:29:56,432 --> 00:29:59,922
I dated you thinking you broke up with that woman.

403
00:29:59,922 --> 00:30:04,352
I never would've dated you if I knew you had a fiancÃ©e.

404
00:30:04,352 --> 00:30:08,332
