405
00:30:08,332 --> 00:30:12,412
Ji Yeong, let's not do this, please.

406
00:30:12,412 --> 00:30:14,792
We're over.

407
00:30:14,792 --> 00:30:16,752
Why are you doing this?

408
00:30:19,892 --> 00:30:21,722
We're over?

409
00:30:21,722 --> 00:30:24,302
Is it over if you say it is?

410
00:30:24,302 --> 00:30:26,432
I'm not done with you, I said.

411
00:30:26,432 --> 00:30:30,632
- It's not over yet, then. It isn't. 
 - Let go of me.

412
00:30:30,632 --> 00:30:32,712
Would you let go if you were me?

413
00:30:32,712 --> 00:30:36,982
Let's talk more somewhere quiet.

414
00:30:38,222 --> 00:30:40,542
Let go, I said!

415
00:30:42,412 --> 00:30:44,512
Let go of her.

416
00:30:45,622 --> 00:30:48,332
Ji Yeong said no.

417
00:30:48,332 --> 00:30:50,062
How dare you butt in?

418
00:30:50,062 --> 00:30:52,262
Why do you keep butting in?

419
00:30:53,252 --> 00:30:54,852
Director!

420
00:30:54,852 --> 00:30:57,432
Why are you doing this now...

421
00:31:05,562 --> 00:31:07,542
- Ji Yeong! 
 - Hey.

422
00:31:07,542 --> 00:31:10,102
Where are you going after hitting me?

423
00:31:24,632 --> 00:31:26,752
What happened to your face, Jin Dan?

424
00:31:26,752 --> 00:31:29,082
Did you get into a fight?

425
00:31:29,082 --> 00:31:31,272
Goodness. Of course not.

426
00:31:31,272 --> 00:31:33,852
He's not a little kid or anything.

427
00:31:33,852 --> 00:31:35,732
He ran into a glass door.

428
00:31:35,732 --> 00:31:37,322
I do that sometimes, too.

429
00:31:37,322 --> 00:31:39,132
Glass doors are so dangerous.

430
00:31:39,132 --> 00:31:40,782
Even birds run into them and die.

431
00:31:40,782 --> 00:31:45,272
Chairman Gong, what important announcement do you have for everyone?

432
00:31:45,272 --> 00:31:48,472
Jin Dan is here now. Tell us.

433
00:31:51,122 --> 00:31:54,142
It's regarding the adoption.

434
00:31:56,932 --> 00:31:59,952
Are you reconsidering it?

435
00:31:59,952 --> 00:32:02,452
Yes, what else can you do?

436
00:32:02,452 --> 00:32:04,592
I'm glad you're doing this.

437
00:32:04,592 --> 00:32:07,172
I'm not adopting Jin Dan,

438
00:32:07,172 --> 00:32:11,092
but we need someone to protect Ma Ri and the company.

439
00:32:11,092 --> 00:32:13,492
So, I decided to adopt someone else.

440
00:32:13,492 --> 00:32:15,692
What do you mean?

441
00:32:15,692 --> 00:32:20,142
There's no other Gong but Jin Dan. Who are you trying to adopt?

442
00:32:20,142 --> 00:32:24,932
I want to adopt Go Pil Sung, Ma Ri's brother.

443
00:32:24,932 --> 00:32:27,712
- As long as Pil Sung and his family agree. 
 - Whatâ€”

