00:32:27,712 --> 00:32:29,222
What did you say?

445
00:32:29,222 --> 00:32:32,612
Hyung, what are you talking about?

446
00:32:32,612 --> 00:32:34,992
Did you say, "Go Pil Sung" just now?

447
00:32:34,992 --> 00:32:39,032
Chairman Gong, are you in your right mind?

448
00:32:39,032 --> 00:32:40,772
