450
00:32:44,782 --> 00:32:47,922
It's not even Jin Dan, but a strange from Go family?

451
00:32:47,922 --> 00:32:52,292
Will you give Soo Yeon's illegitimate child everything we have?

452
00:32:52,292 --> 00:32:55,752
He's not a stranger. He's Ma Ri's older brother.

453
00:32:55,752 --> 00:32:59,522
I decided after considering everything.

454
00:33:01,772 --> 00:33:04,442
