455
00:33:04,442 --> 00:33:06,122
Do whatever you want!

456
00:33:06,122 --> 00:33:10,122
Give APP Group to a Go or Choi! Do whatever!

457
00:33:10,122 --> 00:33:14,652
Aigoo, aigoo... aigoo... aigoo, aigoo...

458
00:33:14,652 --> 00:33:16,772
Gosh, my head. My head...

459
00:33:16,772 --> 00:33:19,262
Auntie.

460
00:33:31,262 --> 00:33:33,012
What?

461
00:33:33,012 --> 00:33:36,002
Adopt Go Pil Sung?

462
00:33:36,002 --> 00:33:40,052
What kind of bullshit is this?

463
00:33:47,222 --> 00:33:49,182
What are you looking at?

464
00:33:50,242 --> 00:33:52,702
What the hell are you looking at!

465
00:34:00,142 --> 00:34:02,862
Hey, Gong Jin Taek!

466
00:34:02,862 --> 00:34:05,112
Come out, Gong Jin Taek!

467
00:34:05,112 --> 00:34:07,472
Gong Jin Taek!

468
00:34:10,122 --> 00:34:12,622
Jin Dan, what are you doing?

469
00:34:12,622 --> 00:34:16,012
Go to bed if you got drunk.

470
00:34:16,012 --> 00:34:20,522
Hey, Gong Jin Taek. Are you the only son of Gong Dae Gil?

471
00:34:20,522 --> 00:34:23,572
I'm also Gong Dae Gil's son, my father.

472
00:34:23,572 --> 00:34:27,522
What gives you the right to look down on me?

473
00:34:27,522 --> 00:34:30,772
Is it because my mom was his mistress? Huh?

474
00:34:30,772 --> 00:34:35,852
I'm a Gong, but how could you adopt Go Pil Sung as your son?

475
00:34:35,852 --> 00:34:38,212
Am I inferior to him?

476
00:34:38,212 --> 00:34:40,062
I'm your brother.

477
00:34:40,062 --> 00:34:42,832
I'm a brother who shares blood with you!

478
00:34:44,902 --> 00:34:48,352
Gosh, why are you doing this? Come on.

479
00:34:50,182 --> 00:34:55,092
Have you ever looked at me kindly since I was a kid?

480
00:34:55,092 --> 00:34:58,782
I followed you around because I liked you.

481
00:34:58,782 --> 00:35:02,642
How could you look down on me since then?

482
00:35:02,642 --> 00:35:06,492
Hey, Gong Jin Taek. You can't do this.

483
00:35:06,492 --> 00:35:10,642
My father, Chairman Gong Dae Gil, is watching us from heaven right now!

484
00:35:10,642 --> 00:35:13,522
Don't do this. That's enough, Jin Dan.

485
00:35:13,522 --> 00:35:15,542
Mom.

486
00:35:16,442 --> 00:35:19,082
