488
00:35:25,992 --> 00:35:30,782
I would've felt less lonely if I had grown up in a poor family!

489
00:35:30,782 --> 00:35:33,662
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

490
00:35:33,662 --> 00:35:37,457
Let's go upstairs now, Jin Dan.

491
00:35:37,457 --> 00:35:38,997
Let's go.

492
00:35:40,822 --> 00:35:44,912
Mom... What the hell is this?

493
00:35:44,912 --> 00:35:47,202
- I'm so lonely, Mom. 
 - Chairman Gong,

494
00:35:47,202 --> 00:35:50,002
you can't do this.

495
00:35:51,042 --> 00:35:53,582
I know Jin Dan isn't good enough,

496
00:35:53,582 --> 00:35:57,502
