513
00:38:05,242 --> 00:38:07,842
I thought you sounded so cute.

514
00:38:07,842 --> 00:38:11,262
You're the one who laughed first.

515
00:38:11,262 --> 00:38:13,612
When did I do that?

516
00:38:16,992 --> 00:38:18,852
I...

517
00:38:18,852 --> 00:38:21,542
I'll prepare for the shoot now.

518
00:38:21,542 --> 00:38:23,522
Gosh!

519
00:38:28,742 --> 00:38:31,352
You didn't fall because of your oppa, right?

520
00:38:32,152 --> 00:38:35,262
Your head would've split open without me.

521
00:38:36,162 --> 00:38:40,412
